This message contains status information about the batching buffer.It can be polled and it can also be sent by the receiver as a response to aUBX-LOG-RETRIEVEBATCH message before the UBX-LOG-BATCH messages.See Data Batching for more information.

column7: Current buffer fill level, i.e. number of epochscurrently stored
Number of dropped epochs since startupNote: changing the batching configuration willreset this counter.
Number of dropped epochs since lastMON-BATCH message
The next retrieved UBX-LOG-BATCH will havethis msgCnt value.
